1
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,480
What are you doing?

2
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:22,159
Looking up info on Wild Wolves

3
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:23,480
to study you.

4
00:01:24,359 --> 00:01:25,000
No need.

5
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,120
Contract's off.

6
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,599
You can leave tomorrow.

7
00:01:30,439 --> 00:01:31,680
Who says I'm leaving?

8
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,719
My mark's still there.

9
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,879
I need to figure out our connection.

10
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,840
With all these books,

11
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,760
no history on the Wolf Clan?

12
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,480
Belle

13
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,280
to save her father

14
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:52,879
that she took the risk

15
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,280
to hide in a castle with a beast.

16
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:00,519
What about you?

17
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,400
What's your purpose?

18
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,599
Of course, it's to use you.

19
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:05,879
It's simple.

20
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,760
I like you.

21
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:09,800
I want to pursue you.

22
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,599
I've been connected with beasts since I was a child.

23
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,280
The fiercer,

24
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,639
the more I like.

25
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,039
You don't understand the law of the jungle.

26
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:27,639
You'll get killed like this.

27
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,240
So,

28
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,039
the wolf king is caring about me.

29
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:39,080
It's the last warning before farewell.

30
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,759
Are you afraid of thunder?

31
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,439
I'm not.

32
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,479
The wolf's hearing

33
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,159
is more sensitive than that of humans.

34
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:09,680
Don't worry.

35
00:03:10,159 --> 00:03:11,000
I won't laugh at you.

36
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:17,479
Thunder means forest fire.

37
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:19,960
It's our instinct

38
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,599
to avoid disasters.

39
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,439
It seems that

40
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,800
you are always dominated by your instincts.

41
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,599
The brand

42
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,159
is the excuse of your Wolf Clan.

43
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:40,560
The human's explanation is

44
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:42,479
physiological preference.

45
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:30,360
You are not convenient today.

46
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:31,839
I'll let you go.

47
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,920
This is the place in the photo.

48
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,639
Little wildcat.

49
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,160
Your claws are pretty sharp, huh?

50
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,959
Can't make a sound now, can you?

51
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,319
Do you even know

52
00:05:11,399 --> 00:05:12,600
whose turf this is,

53
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:15,160
and who I am?

54
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,000
Who are you?

55
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,439
I'm Lu Zhiyu's girlfriend.

56
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,560
If you lay a hand on me here,

57
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,480
you won't walk out of here alive.

58
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,360
I don't care who your boyfriend is.

59
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:29,279
Take her away.

60
00:05:35,639 --> 00:05:36,720
Go tell Qin Yeren,

61
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,720
he's crossed the line.

62
00:05:46,800 --> 00:05:47,639
What are you doing here?

63
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,759
I heard someone calling my name.

64
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,000
What did he say?

65
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:55,079
Lu Zhiyu's girlfriend.

66
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,120
You have a good nose.

67
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,720
The photo is gone.

68
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,680
So many antiques.

69
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,519
Are they all his secret collections?

70
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:04,759
My dagger.

71
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,839
This is what you're looking for.

72
00:07:32,079 --> 00:07:33,759
Who are you?

73
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,360
Get out!

74
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:51,839
Sir.

75
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:54,839
Sir.

76
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:01,360
Stop.

77
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,399
Stop.

78
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:06,839
Sir.

79
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:07,759
Sir.

80
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,560
I'm so sorry.

81
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,160
Thank you for helping me.

82
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:23,319
But you are so bold.

83
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,519
You are alone in the wild at night.

84
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,160
I almost thought you were a ghost.

85
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:33,919
So, what's your name?

86
00:08:35,519 --> 00:08:37,000
My name is Jiang Yue, the "Yue" in "moon".

87
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:38,039
And you?

88
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:40,399
They all call me

89
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,440
Chen.

90
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:46,679
So, why are you here?

91
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:51,200
Had a fight with your boyfriend?

92
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:56,360
Got it.

93
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,039
You want him

94
00:08:58,639 --> 00:08:59,279
to worry about you.

95
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,879
The most wanted target

96
00:09:11,159 --> 00:09:12,480
is just a girl?

97
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,440
Be nice to my friend.

98
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:17,799
Really?

99
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,080
Look,

100
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,440
your friend seems to have something to say.

101
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:30,600
You're a bounty hunter, right?

102
00:09:31,080 --> 00:09:33,039
I'll pay double to redeem myself.

103
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,960
I'm just a delivery guy.

104
00:09:35,399 --> 00:09:36,240
It's done.

105
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:37,799
I'm leaving.

106
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,600
You don't want the bounty?

107
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:41,840
It's on the house for new friends.

108
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:46,159
Have a good time.

109
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,720
have fun.

110
00:09:49,559 --> 00:09:50,679
You little rascal,

111
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,960
don't let me see you again.

112
00:10:07,639 --> 00:10:08,279
Mr. Qin.
